1. Enumerating network interfaces:
python3 list_network_interfaces.py

2.Finding ip address:
python3 get_interface_ip_address.py --ifname eth0

3. Checking interface status:
python3 find_network_interface_status.py --ifname eth0

4. Detecting inactive machine:
sudo python3 detect_inactive_machines.py --scan-hosts 192.168.1.1-3

5.ICMP ping (row socket):
sudo python3ping_remote_host.py --target-host google.com

6.Ping Using subprocess:
python3 ping_subprocess.py

7. Broadcast packet scanning:
sudo python3 broadcast_scanning.py

8.Packet sniffing using subprocess:
sudo setcap cap_net_raw,cap_net_admin=eip $(which tcpdump)
tcpdump -c 10 -i eth0

9.Basic talent echo server:
chmod +x echo_client.py
sudo python3 echo_client.py 

***Socet programming***
gcc server.c -o server
gcc client.c -o client
ls
./server
./client


